            <title>Google Chrome 改善記憶體控制　可調整自動停用分頁行為</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/google-chrome-performance-controls/software/pc-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-chrome-performance-controls</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/google-chrome-performance-controls/software/pc-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 11:00:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MAC App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PC App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
